	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The problem with Loopy's document and your summary is that they use a special language for representing the effects, but don't define that language. A while back I translated that into a <a href="http://blargg.parodius.com/info/nes_scrolling.txt" class="postlink">form more readable to myself</a>. It defines the language used, the state, and the effect of actions.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
